META DESCRIPTION: On January 10, 2016, the Toys and Children's Products Safety Ordinance (Amendment of Schedules 1 and 2) Notice 2016 was published in the Hong Kong Government Gazette to update the safety standards for toys and some children's products. The new law will come into force on October 1, 2016.
